HG: The two. And after the two?

00:12:35.633 --> 00:12:36.875
Audience member 4: Three.

00:12:36.875 --> 00:12:38.518
HG: Three, and after?

00:12:38.518 --> 00:12:40.484
Audience member 4: Three.
HG: Three.

00:12:40.484 --> 00:12:42.540
Audience member 4: Seven.
HG: Seven.

00:12:42.540 --> 00:12:44.274
Audience member 4: Four.
HG: Four.

00:12:44.274 --> 00:12:46.788
Audience member 4: Two.
HG: Two, and?

00:12:46.788 --> 00:12:48.718
Audience member 4: Q.

00:12:48.718 --> 00:12:52.590
HG: Q like in queen?

00:12:52.590 --> 00:12:54.280
(Applause)

00:12:54.280 --> 00:12:55.590
The queen of clubs!

00:12:55.590 --> 00:12:59.420
All the cards in order, just for you.

00:12:59.420 --> 00:13:00.716
